  "detailed_description": "Init. will test your ability to see through illusion and discover innovative and cerebral challenges that can be solved as simply as changing the way you perceive them.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br>* Over 40 unique and challenging constructs<br>* Bring along a friend and overcome special split-screen objective-based missions<br>* Melt into an ethereal soundtrack and succumb to binaural manipulation<br>* Use 'Root Access' to modify constructs and reveal secret areas by reconstructing the environment around you<br>* Delve deeper into the mysterious Invertica system and discover a terrifying global agenda",
